      importantNote: "<h4>Important Mindset for Improvisation</h4><p><strong>Improvisation is NOT about:</strong></p><ul><li>Playing as many notes as possible</li><li>Running scales up and down</li><li>Showing off technique</li></ul><p><strong>Improvisation IS about:</strong></p><ul><li>Musical expression</li><li>Telling a story</li><li>Connecting with the listener</li><li>Making intentional choices</li></ul><p>Focus on playing fewer notes more meaningfully rather than many notes without purpose.</p>",
